statements.sql: select * from `users` where `id` = 13850 and `users`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
select `payments`.`amount` from `invoices` left join `payments` on `invoices`.`id` = `payments`.`invoice_id` where `invoices`.`currency` = 'USD' and `invoices`.`status` != 'pending'
select `payments`.`amount` from `invoices` left join `payments` on `invoices`.`id` = `payments`.`invoice_id` where `invoices`.`currency` = 'INR' and `invoices`.`status` != 'pending'

select `payments`.`amount` from `invoices` left join `payments` on `invoices`.`id` = `payments`.`invoice_id` where year(`invoices`.`date`) = '2023' and `invoices`.`currency` = 'INR' and `invoices`.`status` != 'pending'

select `payments`.`amount` from `invoices` left join `payments` on `invoices`.`id` = `payments`.`invoice_id` where year(`invoices`.`date`) = '2023' and `invoices`.`currency` = 'USD' and `invoices`.`status` != 'pending'

select `payments`.`amount` from `invoices` left join `payments` on `invoices`.`id` = `payments`.`invoice_id` where year(`invoices`.`date`) = '2023' and month(`invoices`.`date`) = '04' and `invoices`.`currency` = 'INR' and `invoices`.`status` != 'pending'

select `payments`.`amount` from `invoices` left join `payments` on `invoices`.`id` = `payments`.`invoice_id` where year(`invoices`.`date`) = '2023' and month(`invoices`.`date`) = '04' and `invoices`.`currency` = 'USD' and `invoices`.`status` != 'pending'
select count(*) as aggregate from `subscriptions` where `created_at` between '2023-03-25 04:51:32' and '2023-04-23 04:51:32'
select count(*) as aggregate from `subscriptions` where `created_at` = `updated_at` and `created_at` between '2023-03-25 04:51:32' and '2023-04-23 04:51:32'

select `id`, `first_name`, `last_name`, `user_name`, `profile_pic`, `email`, `created_at` from `users` where `active` = 1 and `mobile_verified` = 1 and `users`.`deleted_at` is null order by `created_at` desc limit 20

select COUNT(*) as order_count, `products`.`id` as `product_id`, `orders`.`created_at` as `order_created_at`, `products`.`image` as `product_image`, `products`.`name` as `product_name` from `orders` inner join `products` on `products`.`id` = `orders`.`product` where `order_status` = 'executed' and `orders`.`created_at` > '2023-03-25 04:51:32' group by `products`.`id` order by `order_count` desc, `orders`.`created_at` desc

select `products`.`id` as `product_id`, `orders`.`created_at` as `order_created_at`, `number` as `order_number`, `client`, `orders`.`id` as `order_id`, `products`.`name` as `product_name` from `orders` inner join `products` on `products`.`id` = `orders`.`product` where `orders`.`created_at` > '2023-03-25 04:51:32' and `price_override` > 0 order by `orders`.`id` desc
select `id`, `first_name`, `last_name`, `email`, `user_name` from `users` where `users`.`id` in (13850) and `users`.`deleted_at` is null

select `subscriptions`.`id`, `products`.`id` as `product_id`, `orders`.`number` as `order_number`, `orders`.`id` as `order_id`, `products`.`name` as `product_name`, `subscriptions`.`update_ends_at` as `subscription_ends_at`, `user_id` from `subscriptions` inner join `orders` on `subscriptions`.`order_id` = `orders`.`id` inner join `products` on `products`.`id` = `orders`.`product` where `price_override` > 0 and `update_ends_at` > '2023-04-24 04:51:32' and `update_ends_at` <= '2023-05-24 04:51:32' group by `subscriptions`.`id` order by `subscription_ends_at` asc

select `subscriptions`.`id`, `products`.`id` as `product_id`, `orders`.`number` as `order_number`, `orders`.`id` as `order_id`, `products`.`name` as `product_name`, `subscriptions`.`update_ends_at` as `subscription_ends_at`, `user_id` from `subscriptions` inner join `orders` on `subscriptions`.`order_id` = `orders`.`id` inner join `products` on `products`.`id` = `orders`.`product` where `price_override` > 0 and `update_ends_at` < '2023-04-24 04:51:32' and `update_ends_at` >= '2023-03-25 04:51:32' group by `subscriptions`.`id` order by `subscription_ends_at` asc

select `invoices`.`id` as `invoice_id`, `invoices`.`number` as `invoice_number`, `invoices`.`grand_total`, `invoices`.`status`, SUM(payments.amount) as paid, `invoices`.`user_id`, `currencies`.`code` as `currency_code` from `invoices` left join `currencies` on `invoices`.`currency` = `currencies`.`code` left join `payments` on `invoices`.`id` = `payments`.`invoice_id` where `invoices`.`created_at` > '2023-03-25 04:51:32' and `invoices`.`grand_total` > 0 group by `invoices`.`id` order by `invoices`.`created_at` desc
select `id`, `first_name`, `last_name`, `email`, `user_name` from `users` where `users`.`id` in (13850) and `users`.`deleted_at` is null

select COUNT(*) as order_count, `products`.`id` as `product_id`, `orders`.`created_at` as `order_created_at`, `products`.`image` as `product_image`, `products`.`name` as `product_name` from `orders` inner join `products` on `products`.`id` = `orders`.`product` where `order_status` = 'executed' and `orders`.`created_at` > '2001-01-01 00:00:00' group by `products`.`id` order by `order_count` desc, `orders`.`created_at` desc
select `version` from `subscriptions` order by `version` desc limit 1

select `orders`.`id`, concat(first_name, ' ', last_name) as client_name, `products`.`name` as `product_name`, `products`.`id` as `product_id`, `subscriptions`.`version` as `product_version`, `client` as `client_id`, `subscriptions`.`update_ends_at` as `subscription_ends_at` from `orders` left join `subscriptions` on `orders`.`id` = `subscriptions`.`order_id` left join `users` on `orders`.`client` = `users`.`id` left join `products` on `orders`.`product` = `products`.`id` where `price_override` > 0 and `subscriptions`.`updated_at` > '2023-03-25 04:51:32' and `subscriptions`.`update_ends_at` < '2023-05-24 04:51:32' and `subscriptions`.`version` < 'v6.0.2' and `subscriptions`.`version` is not null and `subscriptions`.`version` != '' order by `subscription_ends_at` desc limit 30
select count(*) as aggregate from `orders` where `created_at` between '2023-03-25 04:51:32' and '2023-04-24 04:51:32'
select count(*) as aggregate from `orders` where `price_override` > 0 and `created_at` between '2023-03-25 04:51:32' and '2023-04-24 04:51:32'
select `version` from `subscriptions` group by `version` order by `version` desc limit 1 offset 1
select `version` from `subscriptions` where `version` is not null and `version` != '' group by `version` order by `update_ends_at` asc limit 1
